        "text": "LA PAZ told RYAN that two men whom he interviewed at Kenna, New Mexico, who\nhad observed phenomena which appeared to have disseminated near Tatum, New\nMexico, had informed him \"nothing will be found\". LA PAZ stated he attached\nsignificance to the above statement and that the men apparently had some\nknowledge that the phenomena was not a meteorite."
      },
      "translation": {
